      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NICKO JACK (2) broke from the inside draw and filled a minor placing last start, beaten only 1.75 lengths (20.63) behind Where's Ivy at this track. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Nicely placed to grab a well-deserved win. MOUNT FUJI (8) comes off an average performance last start when fifth at this track over 365m behind Where's Fernando (20.82) in a NG. Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. Should be in this for a long way. KUNG FU BAY (4) held his own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only a neck (20.47) behind Kicking Bins at this track. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Bold showing expected. MINNIE MONSTER (1) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.",
